{"about_the_game":"<img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1740230/extras/3timesdacashar.png?t=1720855180\" /><br>After a game cartridge falls from the sky, you wake up in a strange new world full of big heads, strawberries, manga, and cake!  In this world, there are two sides to every soul: Main and Invert!<br><br>Welcome to Furquest - a cute RPG about loving your friends!<br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1740230/extras/Demo_Features.png?t=1720855180\" /><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>A cute story about a shaggy dog, a lonely bunny, a goofy horse and a... wolf. becoming best friends!<br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1740230/extras/group_dance.gif?t=1720855180\" /><br></li><li>Every enemy in Furquest has their own unique minigame for you to play!<br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1740230/extras/enemies.gif?t=1720855180\" /><br></li><li>Tons of games to play in the world - carve pumpkins, decorate snow people, read manga, play basketball + more!<br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1740230/extras/basket.gif?t=1720855180\" /><br></li><li>Unique boss fights covering a range of different genres from cooking games to visual novels!<br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1740230/extras/Spinzo_and_rat_dance.gif?t=1720855180\" /><br></li><li>A sweet art style and a sour soundtrack!<br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1740230/extras/boombox.gif?t=1720855180\" /></li></ul><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1740230/extras/5vlSFj.png?t=1720855180\" /><br><i>In this world, there are two sides to every coin.  Although, while that is also true for your world...<br><br>In this world, there are two sides to every soul: MAIN and INVERT.  A 'good' Main will be matched by an 'evil' Invert.  A 'happy' Main will be matched by an 'unhappy' Invert, and so on.<br><br>However...<br><br>By stealing the other's soul, the soul thief will transform into an incredibly powerful new form, a HERO SOUL!<br><br>After X,000 years of Soul Wars, Prince Aef has made friendship itself a crime as a last ditch effort to separate the groups and protect their souls.<br><br>One fateful day, a rather strange puppy wakes up in this world. This is their story... er, quest!</i><br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1740230/extras/6.png?t=1720855180\" />","background":"https://store.akamai.steamstatic.com/images/storepagebackground/app/1740230?t=1720855180","background_raw":"https://store.akamai.steamstatic.com/images/storepagebackground/app/1740230?t=1720855180","capsule_image":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1740230/capsule_231x87.jpg?t=1720855180","capsule_imagev5":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1740230/capsule_184x69.jpg?t=1720855180","categories":[{"description":"Single-player","id":2},{"description":"Full controller support","id":28},{"description":"Captions available","id":13},{"description":"Family Sharing","id":62}],"content_descriptors":{"ids":[],"notes":null},"controller_support":"full","detailed_description":"<img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1740230/extras/3timesdacashar.png?t=1720855180\" /><br>After a game cartridge falls from the sky, you wake up in a strange new world full of big heads, strawberries, manga, and cake!  In this world, there are two sides to every soul: Main and Invert!<br><br>Welcome to Furquest - a cute RPG about loving your friends!<br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" s